JdbcTemplate

Responsible for auto creation of connection and release of connection

handles exception more efficiently with msg
perform all ops like insertion,deletion updation

To create a db connection we need
db username,password,driverclassname these all are properties of interface DataSource
DriverManagerDataSource is the implementation class of DataSource

JdbcTempate class has a property datasource
pass the obj of implemetaion class of DataSource to this property and
voila JOB is done

use this jdbctemplate to perform all ops
